{"tid":206500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（有錢人精過你？）名滿山、壹何文田連環撻大定","createTime":"2017-04-18T11:54:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T12:53:43.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"13e1093795bdfd3a5da44117756c622e1e4da648","tid":206500,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T11:54:27.000Z","msg":"據成交紀錄冊顯示，有一批去年入市的買家，近期接連縮沙，輸定離場。<br />\n<br />\n會德豐(020)何文田One Homantin首次出現撻大定個案，涉及2伙單位&hellip;&hellip;去年4月及11月&hellip;&hellip;成交，&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;料2名買家各損失近83萬及超過156萬元定金。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，嘉里(683)屯門滿名山亦有2名買家去年7月&hellip;&hellip;各自購買樓盤兩房單位，交易本月告吹，估計發展商共殺定超過140萬元。"},{"pid":"803fbfc7a01784117218c8a3cb464dcf0a758596","tid":206500,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T11:56:54.000Z","msg":"條數究竟點計呢？"},{"pid":"3993d8c290e5d084bde98e83e4c4150cea2068bd","tid":206500,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T12:53:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}